                        <cite>- Dr. Carlos Rodriguez, Principal Investigator</cite>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feedback-quote">
                        <blockquote>
                            "SPIN's global network enabled us to recruit patients from 15 countries for our rare disease study."
                        </blockquote>
                        <cite>- Dr. Emma Thompson, Lead Researcher</cite>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

